org.knime.core.node.interactive

Interface InteractiveNode<REP extends ViewContent,VAL extends ViewContent>

  • Type Parameters:
    REP - The concrete class of the WebViewContent acting as representation of the view.
    VAL - The concrete class of the WebViewContent acting as value of the view.
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    WizardNode<REP,VAL>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    InteractiveHiLiteCollectorNodeModel

    public interface InteractiveNode<REP extends ViewContent,VAL extends ViewContent>
    Interface for NodeModels that support interactive views and repeated execution when the view has been modified by the user.
    Since:
    2.8
    Author:
    B. Wiswedel, Th. Gabriel, M. Berthold
